HEADWORD: Insomnia
<hw>In*som"ni*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr.
<ets>insomnis</ets> sleepless; pref. <ets>in-</ets> not +
<ets>somnus</ets> sleep.]</ety> <def>Lack of sleep; inability to sleep,
especially when chronic; wakefulness; sleeplessness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insomnious</ent>⟦br⟧
